      [
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          "They’re supporting "
        ],
        [
          0,
          [
            4
          ],
          1,
          "12 news organisations with grants"
        ],
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          " - up to €50,000 each. They selected with a fairly robust set of criteria, and only after the collection of a solid evidence base about each organisation. That baseline of information will allow the Accelerator team to track how the supported organisations have managed to hit their objectives. The partners fill in progress and impact forms as they go, that allows them to share information through the scheme with other supported organisations."
        ]
      ]
    ],
    [
      1,
      "p",
      [
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          "The Accelerator runs a mix of closed and open events - with a big one planned for Berlin in June. They’re developing an ambassador network, of six or seven organisation in countries where they’re not directly supporting anyone with grants."
        ]
      ]
    ],
